## Hints for Future Agents
- The fetch command needs single quotes around 'refs/notes/*:refs/notes/*'
  in package.json so the shell glob doesn't expand. JSON-escaping inside
  package.json's "scripts" map handles this fine; bun and npm both pass
  the script through as one string.
- `git push origin refs/notes/commits` is idempotent — running it when
  there's nothing new just returns "Everything up-to-date".

